                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>The incipit of Text I is on <locus target="#16r">16r</locus>.</note>
                     <note>The text was written by two scribes who probably worked at the same time
                        (s. the change of hand within the section, ʾArganon za-qadāmit, <locus from="97vb" to="98ra">97vb-98ra</locus>). However, it cannot be excluded
                        that quire XIII and XIV (hand b) were added later to substitute the part of
                        the text which had been lost.</note>
                  </msItem>
