                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#00"/>
                           <desc> </desc>
                           <desc>f.111vb: Supplication for the donor.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">f.111vb: ጸሎታ፡ ወበረከታ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ገብራ ሥልጣነ፡
