                           <quote xml:lang="en">f.111vb: May her prayer and blessing be with her
                              servant Śǝlṭanä Krǝstos, Qāla Mäläkot. </quote>
                           <note> Written in a secondary (later?) hand. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
